snippet.title: Battlefront Plus V9 - Community Update
snippet.description:
Check out the Battlefront Plus website! https://battlefront.plus/

Join our Discord to keep up to date on Battlefront Plus and hang out with the devs! https://discord.gg/99VtTgFBqq
Consider supporting me by donating to my Ko-fi! https://ko-fi.com/thespartancv

Battlefront Plus V9 is a large Quality of Life update that sets the stage for our greatest update yet.

Check out the fully detailed Community Update here: https://battlefront.plus/community-updates/v9/

You can find Battlefront+ at the following link:
https://www.nexusmods.com/starwarsbattlefront22017/mods/7592
